n the deteriorating condition of the lake and changing LULC. Our findings indicate that changing LULC of the lake's catchment is one of the critical factors that has significantly contributed toward the deteriorating ecology and water quality of the Dal Lake. This study shall contribute toward the development of the robust conservation strategy in order to save this urban lake from its untimely death.
