ork Conditionsfavorable political and legal conditions supporting commercialization. This article summarizes the insights gained and the lessons learned from success stories and failures in NewSpace. It presents the recommendations for strategies as to how NewSpace can be successful in Europe and, in particular, in Germany. Given the growing relevance of NewSpace, these insights are of high interest to stakeholders and decision makers worldwide.
